    "description": "In &quot;Marcux: Alien Invasion in the Medieval Era,&quot; you take on the role of a blacksmith who discovers a crashed alien spaceship in a cave near his village. Upon donning the extraterrestrial armor found there, you unleash an alien invasion in the midst of the medieval era. Your objective is to fight against these extraterrestrial enemies to rescue your daughter, who has been kidnapped by these beings.<br><br>In this action-platformer game with elements of stealth and exploration, you will face different enemies and bosses, solve puzzles, and overcome the obstacles that arise in your path. Will you be able to reach the end and defeat this alien invasion?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/a35f34e9154fcdcb6cb45f2597c80b31.poster.avif?t=1762793416\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/a35f34e9154fcdcb6cb45f2597c80b31.webm?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/a35f34e9154fcdcb6cb45f2597c80b31.mp4?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/556a3ce68c691fbb3a49224ecb18b3a1.poster.avif?t=1762793416\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/556a3ce68c691fbb3a49224ecb18b3a1.webm?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/556a3ce68c691fbb3a49224ecb18b3a1.mp4?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Traditional 2D animation brings to life a medieval world filled with villagers, biomechanical monsters, and stunning landscapes.</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A challenging game that offers constant challenges, always staying fair and rewarding the player's skill and strategy.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/fe5122859ff7dbcc9ad63a4d011a44b7.poster.avif?t=1762793416\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/fe5122859ff7dbcc9ad63a4d011a44b7.webm?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/fe5122859ff7dbcc9ad63a4d011a44b7.mp4?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/5087d3708a59921d9ed682ace2d2e891.poster.avif?t=1762793416\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/5087d3708a59921d9ed682ace2d2e891.webm?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108040/extras/5087d3708a59921d9ed682ace2d2e891.mp4?t=1762793416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Find and unlock powerful new abilities with the alien armor to strengthen Marcux and access new areas.</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Speak to a variety of characters, from villagers affected by the invasion to other heroes and allies, for information and help.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.ste